    "body": "The `account import` command calls [`LoadECDSA`](https://github.com/ethereum/go-ethereum/blob/master/crypto/crypto.go#L159) which calls `hex.DecodeString(string(buf))` on the buffer. That one does not like `0x` prefix, but wants unprefixed hexdata. \r\n\r\nSounds very dangerous if you're building a centralilzed system where you can access other users wallets, I hope that's not what you're aiming to do. ",
